{"tid":2435824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為宣佈養豬  要為廣大中國人養好豬","createTime":"2021-03-06T14:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T15:36:41.000Z","uid":391580,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1fba9bada59cb11ccc74e494c6b01651ffb50b28","tid":2435824,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T14:17:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eShJRtA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeShJRtA.jpg&h=06a05361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日華為「養豬」一事引起熱議，華為機器視覺業務總裁段愛國日前在微博寫道，華為將涉足智慧養殖業，發佈智慧養豬解決方案。這也是繼網易、京東、阿里巴巴後，又一家科技巨頭宣布進軍養豬業。<br />\n<br />\n近日，段愛國在接受採訪時表示，華為並不是要涉足養豬業務本身，而是要幫助企業養好豬。<br />\n<br />\n具體來說，就是通過雲、AI等技術，來幫助養殖業降本增效。他補充道，養殖業相比其它行業，對AI的技術的應用較為落後，「智慧養豬只是我們用視頻、雲服務賦能千行百業的一個場景而已，2020年一些大型的養豬企業找到我們，我們在進行一起的聯創、賦能，養豬企業和別的企業沒什麼其他的區別，就是人工智慧在場景化的應用。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">鴻蒙呢</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbd8b337cfe467fd88e879a46d7eba7bb4adae2","tid":2435824,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T14:22:27.000Z","msg":"依家咪搞緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ca16bbc96d2d52ab26b9594b822cc053fa7320","tid":2435824,"uid":2583,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"14億隻智能養豬"},{"pid":"016d4077e7afcc57530c61e7b6a087f92f029340","tid":2435824,"uid":43809,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T14:38:21.000Z","msg":"華為5豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1a1f331acea3ea5820a2df81fd7614abff649f","tid":2435824,"uid":32675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T14:50:43.000Z","msg":"一路都幫中共手養支那豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2551da78e9a2e4f27c9c66b6ce9e17bee49487f9","tid":2435824,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T14:51:45.000Z","msg":"支那人做支那豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4b28e91235473b9a857ed8132b021dde84ec50","tid":2435824,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T14:53:38.000Z","msg":"咁ai,big data,cloud 又真係萬能tech<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b8434f207feaec09268373add329d625fb4523","tid":2435824,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T15:26:51.000Z","msg":"本身都14億隻"},{"pid":"a0300665b1bbc07d003b189011ef94cd4ab92fb7","tid":2435824,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"煙幕嚟咋，不過其實屌米都可以變華為，共產黨一聲就搞掂"}]}